        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> Here is what I have heard so far. I do not know how much is accurate, but I am curious to find out. If you can verify, or discount any of these things or add information please do.</P><P>I heard that the Sleeper is basically the uber dragon of EQ. That he lives in Velious somewheres. That if you wake him up he rampages through Velious wiping out entire zones then goes back to sleep. That he has never been killed on any server. That a group of guilds came close(like 25% health left) but were all kicked off by a GM or something for using an exploit to do so. That once he is awoken on a given server and gone on his rampage that he can never be awoken on that server again.</P><P>That last part seemed a bit hokey to me when I was told about it, so I decided to ask around about the other aspects as well as find out if that part is true or not. =)</P><P><BR><a target="new"  href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=117251">Talanor S`Tox</a><BR>Necromancer of Innoruuk</P><P><a target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=116028">Tazuuk</a><BR>Necromancer of Cazic Thule<BR></font></td>

