         Ack! That blows goats. Why have a monster that can only ever be activated one time? I could see having an insanley long respawn rate. For instance say that it takes the other dragons a very long time to track his ass down and re-imprision him. I could see having a respawn of a couple months even. But one shot ever for each server is pretty lame. It means that people like me that didn't start playing EQ until recently will probably never have a chance at that cool gear you mentioned. I wonder if Star Wars Galaxies will be worth playing? Then maybe I can get in at the start and have a shot at the uber gear before it all gets nerfed, perma-camped, or removed from the game midstream.</P><P></P><P><a target="new"  href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=117251">Talanor S`Tox</a><BR>Necromancer of Innoruuk</P><P><a target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=116028">Tazuuk</a><BR>Necromancer of Cazic Thule<BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
